    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Perisindus">Perisundo</name></persName>, abitator in
                        locho <placeName ref="#places/1011">Veccliano</placeName>, filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Sunderadus">Sunderadi</name></persName> vende a
                            <persName ref="#people/3305" key="#Bishops">Hieremias</persName> gratia
                        Dei huius <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68">sancte Lucane
                            ecclesie</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, idest res mea illa quas abeo in loco ubi
                        vocitatur <placeName ref="#places/1011">Lintablo</placeName>, prope
                            <placeName ref="#places/1011" key="#Confinia #Wood #Bridges/pontoons"
                                ><rs key="#Wood #Bridges/pontoons">Ponte de
                            Lignaria</rs></placeName>, quod sunt <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">sex petie de terra</rs> et una <rs
                            key="#Wine">petia de vinea</rs>; et <rs key="#Confinia">est tenente</rs>
                        una ex ipse petie de terra uno capo in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio
                            Auserclo</rs>, alio capo tene in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alto
                        uno tene in terra de filii <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >quondam <name ref="Coccia">Coccie</name></persName>; et ille alia petia
                        de terra que vocitatur <placeName key="#Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            ref="#places/1011">ad <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >Padule</rs></placeName>, est tenentes uno capo in via, et alio capo
                        tene in vinea de filii Cocie, lato uno tene in <placeName
                            key="#Cisterns/pits" ref="#places/1011"><rs key="#Cisterns/pits"
                                >Ducaria</rs></placeName>; et ille tertia petia de terra vocitatur
                        ad <placeName key="#Areas #Confinia" ref="#places/1011">Area</placeName>, et
                        est tenente uno capo in via, alio in <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >Padule</rs>, lato uno tene in terra <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Consortes/shared_possessions"><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominichi</name></persName> et de <rs
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortibus</rs> suis; et ille petie
                        de vinea et tres petie de terra sunt ad uno tenente; et ipse vinea est
                        tenente uno capo in fossa, et alio capo tenet in via quod est carraria; et
                        ipse terra uno capo tene in via publica, lateras sunt tenentes in <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra domni
                            regi</rs>; petie ipse de terris et vineis (…) cum cesis et fossis seo
                        omnibus arboribus suis , sive aliis petiis de terris et pratis (…) omnia
                        quantum mihi in denominatis locis et finibus ipsius locis est pertinentes
                        (…). Simul et vindo (…) una petia de terra mea in locho <placeName
                            ref="#places/421" key="#Confinia #Rivers #Wine #Roads"
                        >Arena</placeName>, qui uno capo est tenente in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio
                            Tubra</rs>, et alio capo tene in <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Wine"><name ref="Radulfus"
                            >Rattolfi</name></persName> et in terra de filii <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">quondam <name ref="Gunderadus"
                                >Gunderadi</name></persName>, lato uno tene in <rs key="#Roads"
                            >carraria</rs> (…). Prezzo: argentum soledos triginta in prefinito. Pena
                        in duplum. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Bishops">Luca</placeName>.
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adroaldus"
                            >Atrualdus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive la cartula.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Allo">Aloni</name></persName><rs
                            key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Walpertus">Vualpertus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Albertus">Alpertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus"
                            >Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Alisso"
                                >Alisi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name
                                ref="Teofridus">Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Imelfredus">Himalfridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Albertus">Alpertus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
